description:
*DISCLAIMER*- ( TO BE CLEAR this is a inside thing with some of the livestreamers on twitch. this happened off stream.)
I am tired of whatever false rumor is circulating about me on Twitch from these livestreamers who know nothing about this situation involving Kimmee/Kimcella and Ice Poseidon. I am adressing literally EVERYTHING that happened during the butler stream. AND EVERYTHING afterwards that i have heard about me and I have clips of a few streamers talking about me very directly after I considered myself NOT to be a person of interest apparently I was wrong. 
TLDR, Someone misunderstood why I was alone with Ice poseidon's girlfriend. She was dumb as a rock to not consider automatic lights the garage as so was I. I didn't expect her to go to where i was sitting in the garage. They definitley took that situation and ran with it. 
And there are other things that i need to address with some situations that happened while i was working uber with esfandtv, qt cinderella, and the austin show.
and then there is a clip with imjasmine that proved that there was a rumor going around about me. 

i dont know what else to add here I literally need to get back to working uber.
Obviously this was harming my reputation, so I needed to get this over with; settle it; and get back to work. I hope I get to finish all my projects by the end of the year.
